Big news in India Fintech
2022-06-08 21:35:26
"RBI allows UPI payment via credit cards, if it is executed well, India will have the most potent payments infrastructure in this era.

Now the question is what will happen to credit card companies whose main incomes come from settlement fees. 

And for now, it works only with RuPay cards, Hope it is not just a promotion."
